&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Do you like a challenge and want to be in a team that are making a real difference to people&#39;s lives?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic self motivated Band 5 Staff Nurse who is ready for an exciting new experience to join a dynamic Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Working at Milton Grange the role will involve working with patients and other health care professionals to provide a holistic approach to patient care, thereby facilitating early discharge from hospital, prevent hospital admissions and aid patients to stay independent in their own home for as long as possible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;At Milton Grange we focus on short term generic rehabilitation working within Adult Social Care in a good supportive environment. For staff this gives unequalled scope for joint working, skill sharing and learning in a supportive environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
